  "title": "RPM Ep. 51 | Now is the Time for Infrastructure Secondaries With Tim Rees",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>StepStone Group- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2025-07-11T14:02:14+00:00\" title=\"Friday, July 11, 2025 - 14:02\">Fri, 07/11/2025 - 14:02</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">RPM Ep. 51 | Now is the Time for Infrastructure Secondaries With Tim Rees</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"Featured-large.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-07/Featured-large.jpg.jpeg\" height=\"381\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-07/Featured-large.jpg.jpeg\" width=\"908\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p>In this episode of RPM, <a href=\"https://www.stepstonegroup.com/members/tim-rees/\">Tim Rees</a>, a London-based Partner on StepStone’s Infrastructure and Real Assets team, joins co-host <a href=\"https://www.stepstonegroup.com/members/michael-venne/\">Michael Venne</a> to discuss the rapid growth of infrastructure secondaries and why the market is gaining momentum. They cover:</p><ul><li>Growth of infrastructure asset class (00:51)</li><li>Scale of the secondary market (03:26)</li><li>Drivers of growth in infra secondaries (05:19)</li><li>Synergies from primaries and co-investments (09:36)</li><li>Advice for new investors (19:39)</li><li>Diversification and other considerations (22:23)<br/> </li></ul><p></p><p>Read the transcript .</p><p>RPM is available on <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/rpm-reflections-on-private-markets/id1537055419\">Apple Podcasts</a> and <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/1xZBHwyP2Bx6RRkMJKXOaP\">Spotify</a>—anywhere you normally get your podcasts. Subscribe today! </p><div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items\"><div class=\"field__item\"><h3>The InsuranceAUM.com podcast is available on</h3><div class=\"btns-wrapper\"> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6WIbsYrL1BXuJMPsZXSk8R\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn2.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/insuranceaum-com/id1500643401\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn3.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/InsuranceAUM-com/dp/B08K57V1D6\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/Frame%20366%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@InsuranceAUMCommunity\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/frame_366%20%281%29%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-4-lg\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><h4>Share this post</h4> <span class=\"a2a_kit 